entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You recovered some stolen goods from a group of thugs known as Braggan's Fist.
entries.journal_entry_description: Recover some stolen goods from the Braggan's Fist thugs.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Recover the stolen goods from the Braggan's Fist hideout. Braggan's Fist are a group of thugs that harass the Tyrena area.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Sgt. Sola Hus with the stolen goods you recovered.
